  (text "Reviewed LB-100 value-bearing schematic inputs:\n- MCU baseline STM32H563VITx LQFP100; STM32H573VITx security alternate; STM32H563RGT6 fallback only after resource reduction.\n- PB_5V_OUT budget: 500 mA sustained allocation; 219.2 mA sustained LB load; 415.2 mA service peak; USB no-back-power boundary.\n- JPB1: exact OUT1_CTL..OUT10_CTL, OUT1_FLT..OUT10_FLT, OUT1_IMON..OUT10_IMON, PB_I2C, CAN1, CAN2, LIN/RS485/UART, and spare binding per LB-100-stm32h563-pin-binding-precheck.csv.\n- CAN1: DNP/open TX route; read-only default; no firmware-only vehicle-CAN TX enable.\n- Services: USB service, BLE, microSD, RTC, FRAM, IMU, lux, SWD, BOOT0, reset, service button."
